12:11.105 --> 12:12.523
Oh. Hm.

12:12.606 --> 12:14.525
Come on, it's gonna be great.

12:14.608 --> 12:16.068
You're gorgeous.

12:17.820 --> 12:19.405
Can you... [mumbles]

12:19.572 --> 12:22.533
