13:21.967 --> 13:23.677
I've got your membership papers.

13:23.761 --> 13:25.179
-You look great.
-Thank you.

13:25.262 --> 13:27.973
Hi, welcome to our shindig.
Good to see you.

13:28.057 --> 13:31.227
-Thanks for having us.
-I thought it was dress to impress.

13:31.310 --> 13:33.938
