13:48.118 --> 13:50.037
-There was a lot of...
-Hi.

13:50.120 --> 13:52.498
-Hi!
-What happened? Do you need a little help?

13:52.581 --> 13:55.793
Don't worry about little old me.
Happy birthday.

13:55.876 --> 13:58.546
-Oh, thank you.
-Wow, this is-- Oh.

13:58.629 --> 14:02.007
Can I use your restroom just to
wash my face and just kind of clean up?

14:02.091 --> 14:04.218
-I feel disgusting.
-Yeah. Right down here.

14:04.301 --> 14:05.177
I'll take her.

14:05.261 --> 14:08.973
This is not what I thought I'd wear
to your 40th but this is what I'm wearing.

14:09.056 --> 14:10.558
Great. You look wonderful.

14:10.641 --> 14:13.185
It's just... in there.

14:13.852 --> 14:15.187
Hand towels on the bottom.

14:15.271 --> 14:17.565
-[Lisa] Yeah. Okay.
-[Ethan] Mm-hmm.

14:19.066 --> 14:22.361
Give me a minute to talk to my wife?
I haven't seen her in a week.

14:22.444 --> 14:25.781
-What's your plan?
-My plan is to tell her about us

14:25.865 --> 14:27.908
before she brings it up first, okay?

14:27.992 --> 14:29.827
Did you see how she just greeted me?

14:29.910 --> 14:31.871
-She definitely knows.
-She doesn't know.

14:31.954 --> 14:33.747
-She knows.
-That is an insane plan.

14:36.584 --> 14:38.085
-Hi.
-Hi.

14:38.794 --> 14:40.004
I need to talk to you.

14:40.546 --> 14:41.839
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

14:43.382 --> 14:45.759
You know what? Let's go get a drink.
We can talk.

14:45.843 --> 14:47.261
-Yeah.
-Okay.

14:49.096 --> 14:50.723
-[whispers] Fuck you.
-Fuck you!

14:52.433 --> 14:53.517
-[Nick] Hey, buddy.
-Hey.

14:53.601 --> 14:56.270
Wow. Don't they sell sunblock
in the Caymans?

14:56.353 --> 14:59.231
Look, I haven't had a second
to talk to Ethan yet.

14:59.315 --> 15:01.901
-Okay? So just...
-Me, neither. I'm so sorry.

15:01.984 --> 15:04.695
I've been wanting to tell him everything
to his face.

15:04.778 --> 15:06.488
Stop it, this isn't funny, okay?

15:06.572 --> 15:10.618
I'm not gonna be able to talk to him until
we leave so let that inform your behavior.

15:10.701 --> 15:11.952
